Project: AI-driven Manufacturing Drawing to 3D Mapping System

Author: Manoj V, Preethi K.M
Year: 2026

Purpose:
This repository was developed as part of a hackathon to demonstrate an AI-based approach 
for extracting Product Manufacturing Information (PMI) from 2D technical drawings and 
mapping it to 3D CAD models.

Scope & Limitations:
- This is a prototype and may not cover all real-world manufacturing scenarios
- Some components may be simplified, mocked, or experimental
- Accuracy and completeness are not guaranteed

